                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/4656" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">HRM-0370</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9613 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">四步打造“人才吸铁石”：浪潮雇主品牌建设</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Four steps to create a “talent magnet”: Inspur Group&#39;s employer brand construction</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">蔡地，胡尊朔，孙涛，王欣桐，韩志玮，刘雨婷</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">山东大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">浪潮集团有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">通讯业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">人力资源部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">12 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">雇主品牌；浪潮；人力资源管理；2020百优案例；微案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Employer Brand; the Inspur Group; Human Resource Management</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业的竞争归根到底是人才的竞争。近年来，雇主品牌因在吸引、保留和激励核心人才方面的作用日益受到国内企业的重视。浪潮集团是我国著名的IT企业，自2010年提出“云计算战略”后，再次驶入高速发展阶段，对优秀人才的需求也日益迫切。最近几年，为了打赢日益激烈的人才抢夺战，浪潮集团开始结合时代和企业需求深化雇主品牌建设，打造独具自身特色的“人才吸铁石”。本案例描述了浪潮集团深化雇主品牌建设的相关背景、具体历程以及下一步所面临的挑战。通过对本案例的分析和讨论，可以系统的深化学生对什么是雇主品牌、雇主品牌为什么重要以及如何建设雇主品牌这三个问题的认识和理解，也可以为企业开展雇主品牌建设提供有益启示。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">The competition of enterprises ultimately becomes the competition of talents. In recent years, the role of employer brand in attracting, retaining and motivating core talents has been increasingly valued by domestic companies. The Inspur Group is a well-known IT company in China. It has entered the stage of high-speed development again since 2010 when the “cloud computing strategy” was proposed, thus it has an increasing demand for excellent talents. In recent years, in order to win the intensifying battle for talents, the Inspur Group has begun to deepen the employer brand construction based on the needs of the time and the company, and create its own unique “talent magnet”. This case describes the relevant background, specific process and the challenges of the Inspur Group deepening employer brand construction. The analyses and discussion in this case can systematically deepen students&#39; understanding of the three issues concerning what is the employer brand, why is the employer brand important, and how to construct the employer brand. It can also provide useful inspiration for companies to carry out employer brand construction.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2019</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《人力资源管理》、《招聘与选拔》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">员工吸引、保留主题</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020-10</td>
                            </tr>
